Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:13.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:15.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:18.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:22.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:26.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:30.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:40.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:44.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:59.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:02.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:11.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:15.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:18.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,150.389)}The Eerie Owl
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,680.389)}Man's Killer X-Rays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.87,0:01:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a standard\NX-ray picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've implanted a more powerful\Nversion of this basic phenomenon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a killer X-Ray\Nemitter—into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Owl Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...\Ngo forth and test your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Owl Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew there\Nwere owls around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard any.\NAnd I go this way every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a little creepy\Nto hear one in the daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, take care.\N- Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Goodbye!\N- Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Shocker cyborg...\NOwl Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up and be my guinea pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the power of\Nmy killer X-rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A smashing success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnesses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer! Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,An owl monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An owl monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not about to fall\Nfor a prank like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a prank! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're just a kid,\Nbut rather than playing pranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you go home\Nand do some studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...\Nwhere did she run off to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her! Find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,An owl monster appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An owl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Shocker plot, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster got my tennis\Ncoach, Mr. Tashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the skeleton to the\Nuniversity lab and investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the test a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby appoint you the head of\NOperation: Clock Tower Detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a map of large clock towers\Nin every city in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at noon,\Nwhen Earth is closest to the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the clocks strike twelve,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll blow the clock\Ntowers up all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This will cause a chain reaction of\Nexplosions in smaller clocks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A literal time bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we accomplish it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The light from your eyes will emit a\Nfrequency to trigger the detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our combatants have already affixed\Nreceivers for that frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,onto large clocks everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I must act immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One location remains\Nwithout a receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You will go there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, Ambassador Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do\Nwith this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Send her to work with\Nthe other prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to construct the\Ntransmitter radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an X-ray that Mr. Tashiro\Nhad taken last year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,after he was in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. This picture\Nmatches the skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Shocker used some\Nspecial method to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same method. X-rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially strong,\Nkiller X-rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The skeleton was\Nconsiderably irradiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go searching with a\NGeiger counter in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs60\c&H000000&\2c&H999C9A&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Mukogaoka Park \N{\c&H2324B0&}Flo{\c&H10A3CE&}wer {\c&H187C18&}Clock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Unusual to hear owls\Naround here these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That little prankster girl\Nmentioned an owl monster, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:27.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Machinery Room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Owl feathers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have gone this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself,\NShocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Meddling fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the power of Owl\NMan's killer X-rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Owl Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for this, Owl Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:56.23,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's talking about\Na skeleton they found
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,near the flower clock\Nin Mukogaoka Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Shocker...\Nwhat are they plotting this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Owl Man got him bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...\Nwe've got some bad news, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Another skeleton appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NShocker's on the move again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. You can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... you okay, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The place he hit me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. I think something's\Njamming the radiation detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that their hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems worth\Ninvestigating, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops... I wonder if we\Ncan lure him out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, we need to make noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry! Hurry! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your plan this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me! Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker thinks nothing\Nof killing their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NHe can only write numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One through twelve...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! It's a clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The radar isn't finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Its completion is imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If the prisoners\Nare slacking on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,execute one as an\Nexample to the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a demonstration\Nof my power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,will inspire you to work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what\Nhappens to slackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer X-ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs60\c&H000000&\2c&H999C9A&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Mukogaoka Park \N{\c&H2324B0&}Flo{\c&H10A3CE&}wer {\c&H187C18&}Clock
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the twelve in the\Ndrawing means twelve o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the X?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably means an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the flower clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check out the\Nmachinery room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:16:04.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Machinery Room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's removed the receiver\Nfrom the flower clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo's caught our trail, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to trigger an explosion\Nusing Owl Man's light-wave frequency...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...\Nthere's more than one location.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. All the clock\Ntowers in the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've laid the ambush\Nfor Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Only five minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's break through, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both the Kamen Rider\Nand the Cyclone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:51.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,were designed to withstand temperatures\Nof several thousand degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The radar is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty seconds to noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We must act before the\NKamen Rider arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When I give the signal,\Nshoot the killer X-rays at this frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty seconds to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. Nine. Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself,\NKamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've crushed your\Nevil scheme this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the Kamen Rider! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!\NYou need to save the prisoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:43.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.35,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:54.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:01.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:12.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:15.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:26.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:29.10,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:33.29,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:44.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:50.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:55.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:58.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:09.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:12.57,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:16.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:19.86,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:23.79,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:30.09,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:33.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.32,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:42.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Owl Man, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer X-rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:59.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider had\Ndefeated Owl Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:02.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would embark on\Neven more wicked schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:04.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:07.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:10.59,Cont,,0,40,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:12.76,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:14.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:16.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous\Nelectrical Namazugiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:21.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami returns to Japan with\Nhis 100,000-volt creation Namazugiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:23.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He and Ambassador Hell\Ninstate a two-front attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,putting Kamen Rider in peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:26.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous\NNamazugiller's Electric Hell."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(508,426)}The Monstrous
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}Namazugiller's Electric Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:40.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:43.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.26,0:23:45.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:50.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:52.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:55.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:03.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:07.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:11.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:15.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eerie Owl\NMan's Killer X-Rays
Comment: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.87,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous\NNamazugiller's Electric Hell
Comment: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.87,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,750.389)}The Monstrous\NNamazugiller's Electric Hell